Distribution ( Fig. 140 ). Present in the Mexican states of Chiapas , Puebla , Oaxaca , Tabasco , and Veracruz , in the following ecoregions (
Dinerstein et al . 2017
): Humid forests of Petén-Veracruz, Sierra de los Tuxtlas, Pine-oak forests of the Sierra Madre of Oaxaca , Pine-oak forests of the Sierra Madre del Sur, Pine-oak forests of the Transmexican Volcanic Belt, and Humid forests of Veracruz . According to the specimens examined, this species may be endemic to Mexico . Altitudinal distribution from 100 to 1390 m .
